---

<Layout title={`${title} - ${subtitle}`}>
	<PageHeader title={title} subtitle={subtitle} button={button}>
		<p class="text-center font-fredericka">
			Season 1 found eighteen castaways taking on the game for the first time in our first season. The game was two days with the premerge playing out on Day 1 and Merge taking on Day 2.
		</p>
	</PageHeader>
